=== TEST 1: request.get_path() returns path component of uri
--- http_config eval: $t::Util::HttpConfig
--- config
    location = /t {
        access_by_lua_block {
            local PDK = require "kong.pdk"
            local pdk = PDK.new()

            ngx.say("normalized path: ", pdk.request.get_path())
        }
    }
--- request
GET /t
--- response_body
normalized path: /t
--- no_error_log
[error]



